        "text": "After working in meet.coop (The online meeting coop) for three years I’m stepping now into a new (resumed) framework: investigating, documenting and convening practical conversations on formación (self-education, capability building and mutuality) for Making a Living Economy. [[Formación work]]"
      },
      "after": "33aed3aae8779357",
      "date": 1700998161614
